- view equipment/items/back to eq (palette issue)
- view equiment/invalid selection (palette issue)
- pray
- search
- examine tiles
- examine and +/- to cycle
- fire and +/- to cycle
- switch palettes (sdl only)
- save and restore to same palette
- switch to ascii (sdl only)
